<v-app>
    <v-parallax
      :src="require('../assets/fracture.jpg')"
      dark
      alt = "background image"
      height = 600
    >
    <v-container>
      <v-toolbar dark color="#FF5722">
        <v-toolbar-title>Reservations</v-toolbar-title>
      </v-toolbar>

    <v-form ref="form" v-model="valid" lazy validation>
      <v-text-field
      dark
      v-model="firstname"
      :rules="rulesForFirstName"
      label="First Name"
      required>
    </v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
    dark
    v-model="lastname"
    :rules="rulesForLastName"
    label="Last Name"
    required>
  </v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
    dark
    v-model="phonenumber"
    :rules="rulesForPhone"
    label="Phone Number"
    required>
  </v-text-field>
  </v-form>
  <v-menu
    dark
    ref="menu"
    :close-on-content-click="false"
    v-model="menu"
    :nudge-right="50"
    lazy
    transition="scale-transition"
    offset-x
    full-width
    min-width="300px">
    <v-text-field
    slot="activator"
    v-model="date"
    label="Choose a Check-In Date"
    prepend-icon="event"
    readonly>
  </v-text-field>
  <v-date-picker dark v-model="date" @input="menu = false">
    <v-spacer></v-spacer>
  </v-date-picker>
</v-menu>
<v-menu
  dark
  ref="menu2"
  :close-on-content-click="false"
  v-model="menu2"
  :nudge-right="50"
  lazy
  transition="scale-transition"
  offset-x
  full-width
  min-width="300px">
  <v-text-field
  slot="activator"
  v-model="date2"
  label="Choose a Check-Out Date"
  prepend-icon="event"
  readonly>
</v-text-field>
<v-date-picker dark v-model="date2" @input="menu2 = false">
  <v-spacer></v-spacer>
</v-date-picker>
</v-menu>
<v-btn dark color="#FF5722">Confirm reservation</v-btn>
</v-container>
</v-parallax>
  </v-app>
